          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group py-5">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-900">What happens in a 1:1 coaching session?</h3>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0 text-neutral-500 transition-transform group-open:rotate-45" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mt-4">
            A session is 60 minutes one-to-one with Viesturs Meikšāns, focused on exactly what you need — structure, body language, voice, storytelling, controlling nerves, or polishing a specific talk. You get direct, personalised feedback on your strengths and weak spots.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group py-5">
